Practica 5 Modulo 9 Playbooks
(Para windows)
nano instalar_notepad.yml
---
- name: Instalacion de Notepad++ en Windows
  hosts: win
  become: yes
  become_method: runas
  become_user: System

  tasks:
    - name: Crear carpeta temporal si no existe
      win_file:
        path: C:\temp
        state: directory

    - name: Descargar instalador de Chocolatey
      win_get_url:
        url: https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1
        dest: C:\temp\install_choco.ps1
      
    - name: Ejecutar instalador de Chocolatey
      win_command: powershell.exe -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\temp\install_choco.ps1
      args:
        creates: C:\ProgramData\chocolatey\bin\choco.exe

    - name: Instalar Notepad++ usando Chocolatey
      win_chocolatey:
        name: notepadplusplus
        state: present
control o y x

(para linux)
nano instalar_nginx.yml
---
- name: Configuracion de servidor Web NGINX
  hosts: linux
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: Instalar NGINX
      apt:
        name: nginx
        state: latest
        update_cache: yes

    - name: Asegurar que NGINX este iniciado y habilitado al arrancar
      service:
        name: nginx
        state: started
        enabled: yes
control o y x
ejecuta: ansible-playbook instalar_notepad.yml
ansible-playbook instalar_nginx.yml
Validación: Abre Firefox en tu Windows e ingresa la IP de tu DigitalOcean (ej. http://137.184.X.X). Deberías ver la página de bienvenida de "Welcome to nginx!"
